00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:25.810
as-tu vu ton cousin ?

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:26.840
Oui, je l'ai fait.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:27.960
[Ye Yuezhi, vice-président de Mare Nubium]

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:29.000
Did Ye Haimeng

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:30.520
